These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, colombian, australian
1. the australian is on the left of the colombian##1
2. the australian is between the brazilian and the colombian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | australian | colombian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, family, fantasy
1. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching family movies and the person watching fantasy movies##2
2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | mystery | family |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, country, gospel
1. the fan of country is between the fan of soul and the fan of gospel##2
2. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | country | soul |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different pets are kept: pony, hedgehog, chinchilla
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the pony##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Pet   | pony | chinchilla | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, 7up
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking soy-milk##2
2. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | hot-chocolate | 7up |

 #################################

 
